{"tid":1716504,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我只係想同你講 我好擔心你。","createTime":"2019-11-13T10:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T13:40:44.000Z","uid":317104,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e083118686dfbd70e33253da0476d06b51f7df15","tid":1716504,"uid":317104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:58:42.000Z","msg":"雖然你唔係我邊個，同你有見過面，但從來無正式face to face咁交流過，平時都只係whatsapp/ig dm傾計。我哋唔係話真係好熟，但都多謝你信任我，發夢都會同我講。我唔可以話我中意你，但我好respect你同時都好擔心你...雖然你唔係讀中大，但係你都同上同落 。就算你因為一啲原因其實唔係好方便去，但你都去。我唔知你係咪因為發夢而少咗聯絡我，所以我唔係好敢成日揾你。但點都好，我只係想係到同你講聲加油！你一定要安全返嚟，我唔想你死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你對我嚟講好重要...當然我都希望所有手足都平平安安返到嚟。紓發完畢<br />\n最後，光復香港，時代革命！香港人，報仇！"},{"pid":"365d901e7ced6a11964647579f04f6a5575006ab","tid":1716504,"uid":129660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 直接同佢講啦..."},{"pid":"5f534d49a213ae2284f9f6de9fc8c823edb3a553","tid":1716504,"uid":317104,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"365d901e7ced6a11964647579f04f6a5575006ab","tid":1716504,"uid":129660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 直接同佢講啦..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"我無嚟個膽量，畢竟我唔係佢邊個，怕打擾到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec80f6f81d44d26b2efa46c7078ff31fcb0de1b","tid":1716504,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:46:38.000Z","msg":"點解要咁驚<br />\n用對朋友既語氣慰問吓佢姐"},{"pid":"bd4aae61ff6dec352497a09fe2f58e692a4572fd","tid":1716504,"uid":335969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f534d49a213ae2284f9f6de9fc8c823edb3a553","tid":1716504,"uid":317104,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0